  "prob_desc_input_spec": "The input consists of four lines with each line describing a road part given in a counter-clockwise order. Each line contains four integers l, s, r, p — for the left, straight, right and pedestrian lights, respectively. The possible values are 0 for red light and 1 for green light.",
